msgid "300"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:265
msgid "多种选择"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:265
msgid "针对请求，服务器可执行多种操作。 服务器可根据请求者 (user agent) 选择一项操作，或提供操作列表供请求者选择。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:266
msgid "301"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:266
msgid "永久移动"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:266
msgid "请求的网页已永久移动到新位置。 服务器返回此响应（对 GET 或 HEAD 请求的响应）时，会自动将请求者转到新位置。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:267
msgid "302"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:267
msgid "临时移动"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:267
#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:271
msgid "服务器目前从不同位置的网页响应请求，但请求者应继续使用原有位置来进行以后的请求。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:268
msgid "303"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:268
msgid "查看其他位置"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:268
msgid "请求者应当对不同的位置使用单独的 GET 请求来检索响应时，服务器返回此代码。"
msgstr ""

